    {\displaystyle |\varphi _{j}\rangle }
   are not assumed to be mutually orthogonal. There will be two corresponding purifications of the mixed state 
  
    
      
        ρ
      
    
    {\displaystyle \rho }
   reading as follows:

Purification 1: 
  
    
      
        
          |
        
        
          Ψ
          
            S
            A
          
          
